title: Grateful Dead Live at Santa Fe Downs on 1982-10-17
lineage: Cassette Master (JVC KD-A55/Super ANRS) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6MHz) > Tascam Hi-Res Editor (WAV 24-bit/96k) > Adobe Audition 2023 > Samplitude Pro X6 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set I
Mississippi Half Step Uptown Toodleloo >
Franklin's Tower >
New Minglewood Blues
Candyman
Me & My Uncle >
Mexicali Blues

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
